<HEADLINE>
<P>
HE'S PUTTING WALSH ON THE DEFENSIVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 With each Stanford defeat and San Francisco 49er victory, it is becoming 
obvious that the real "genius" behind the 49er glory days was George Seifert, 
the defensive coordinator under Bill Walsh. Until Stanford fields a solid 
defense, all the offensive ingenuity in the world will not land Bill Walsh in 
the Rose Bowl. 
</P>
<P>
 ANDREW GROVE 
</P>
<P>
 El Segundo 
</P>
