<DOCNO> LA102994-0028 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 093172 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 29, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
