historically match competitor discounts, were expected to waive them as well. 
The sale applies to tickets bought for flights on Nov. 17, 21, 24 and 25; Dec. 
15, 19, 20, 28 and 29, and Jan. 4-6. The tickets are non-refundable and apply 
only to the 48 contiguous states. The discounts range from 30% to 45%. 
