 The Children's Museum in La Habra is presenting an "Un-haunted House" for 
young children today and Sunday from 11 a.m. to 4 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Storybook characters will lead trick-or-treaters through a "non-scary" Mother 
Gooseland. 
</P>
<P>
 The cost is 50 cents per child. 
</P>
