<TEXT>
<P>
 San Marcos 21, Rio Mesa 14 -- Running back Nathan Ridgell returned a kickoff 
82 yards for one score and rushed 69 yards for another as San Marcos spoiled 
Rio Mesa's homecoming. 
</P>
<P>
