</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP; RIO HONDO LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KEVIN BOLT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 San Marino 21, La Canada 0 -- San Marino's defense notched its second 
consecutive shutout as the Titans (6-2, 3-0) rolled. 
</P>
<P>
 La Canada (3-5, 1-2) was paced by running back Sam Paneno, who gained 84 yards 
in 18 carries. Quarterback James Wolstenholme was limited to only 83 yards 
passing and with two interceptions. KEVIN BOLT 
</P>
