<BYLINE>
<P>
By CHRIS TORRES 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ventura 20, Dos Pueblos 18 -- Running back Aaron Davis of Ventura had 164 
yards in 24 carries, including a 24-yard touchdown run, as visiting Ventura 
withstood a fourth-quarter rally by Dos Pueblos (2-5-1, 1-3-1). 
</P>
<P>
