<P>
SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP; MARMONTE LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LISA GRALL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Thousand Oaks 28, Channel Islands 7 -- Senior Mike Thomas led the Lancers 
(3-4, 2-3) with three touchdowns, scoring on runs of two, three and one yard at 
Channel Islands.He gained 41 yards in 12 carries. 
</P>
<P>
 Bill Sperry led the Lancers with 67 yards in 19 carries. 
</P>
<P>
 Junior Brandon Jackson (66 yards in eight carries) put the game out of reach 
with a 56-yard touchdown run on the second play of the second half, giving 
Thousand Oaks a 21-0 lead. 
</P>
<P>
 The Raiders (1-7, 0-5) scored in the fourth quarter when defensive tackle Red 
Pedrick recovered a fumble at the Lancers' eight-yard line, setting up Tony 
Moore's eight-yard run. LISA GRALL 
</P>
