<HEADLINE>
<P>
CAPISTRANO VALLEY HIRES VOLLEYBALL COACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Capistrano Valley has named Darren Utterback to coach boys' volleyball, the 
school announced Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 Utterback, a former Capistrano Valley student, had been Capistrano Valley 
Christian's coach and has 12 years experience coaching at the club level. He 
has also coached lower-level teams at Mater Dei and Capistrano Valley. 
</P>
